text: Olessya Arslanova (born 13 December 1981) is a Kazakhstani volleyball player. She played at the 2010 Asian Women's Volleyball Cup and 2010 FIVB Volleyball Women's World Championship. She played for VC Zhetysu. == References == Category:1981 births Category:Living people Category:Kazakhstani volleyball players
